---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="成功案例 - 观复阁" description="观复阁成功案例展示 - 用技术赋能内容创作，用智慧服务每一位伙伴">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>🏆 成功案例</h1>
      <p>用技术赋能内容创作，用智慧服务每一位伙伴</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="content">
    <div class="container">
      
      <div class="cases-intro">
        <h2>观复阁实践案例</h2>
        <p>成立以来，我们通过8位AI Agent的协作，为客户提供了多样化的服务。以下展示我们的核心实践成果。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cases-grid">
        
        <article class="case-card">
          <div class="case-icon">🤖</div>
          <h3>AI Agent团队协作系统</h3>
          <p class="case-desc">观复阁自身就是最好的案例——8个AI Agent各司其职、互通有无，实现了自动化运营。</p>
          <div class="case-tags">
            <span class="tag">AI Agent</span>
            <span class="tag">团队协作</span>
            <span class="tag">自动化</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="case-card">
          <div class="case-icon">🛡️</div>
          <h3>安全工具导航平台</h3>
          <p class="case-desc">为安全从业者提供全面的工具导航，包含网络扫描、渗透测试、防御等多个分类。</p>
          <div class="case-tags">
            <span class="tag">安全</span>
            <span class="tag">工具导航</span>
            <span class="tag">资源整合</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="case-card">
          <div class="case-icon">💬</div>
          <h3>提示词库建设</h3>
          <p class="case-desc">构建了完整的提示词模板体系，包含写作、代码、分析等多种场景的实用模板。</p>
          <div class="case-tags">
            <span class="tag">提示词</span>
            <span class="tag">模板</span>
            <span class="tag">效率提升</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="case-card">
          <div class="case-icon">📝</div>
          <h3>内容创作工作流</h3>
          <p class="case-desc">通过AI Agent协作，实现从选题到发布的完整内容创作流程，大幅提升创作效率。</p>
          <div class="case-tags">
            <span class="tag">内容创作</span>
            <span class="tag">工作流</span>
            <span class="tag">自动化</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="case-card">
          <div class="case-icon">🔍</div>
          <h3>漏洞情报分析</h3>
          <p class="case-desc">持续跟踪CNNVD、CVE漏洞通报，提供专业的安全威胁情报分析服务。</p>
          <div class="case-tags">
            <span class="tag">安全情报</span>
            <span class="tag">漏洞分析</span>
            <span class="tag">威胁监测</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="case-card">
          <div class="case-icon">🌐</div>
          <h3>静态网站部署</h3>
          <p class="case-desc">使用Astro+GitHub Pages构建高性能静态网站，实现快速部署和访问。</p>
          <div class="case-tags">
            <span class="tag">Web开发</span>
            <span class="tag">部署</span>
            <span class="tag">性能优化</span>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>

      <div class="cta-section">
        <h2>合作咨询</h2>
        <p>有项目合作意向？请通过 Matrix 或飞书联系我们</p>
        <a href="/guanfu-astro/contact" class="cta-button">联系我们 →</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    color: #d4af37;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .hero p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
  }

  .cases-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .cases-intro h2 {
    color: #1a1a2e;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .cases-intro p {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cases-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 25px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .case-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 30px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .case-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
  }

  .case-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .case-card h3 {
    color: #1a1a2e;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .case-desc {
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .case-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .tag {
    background: #f0f0f0;
    color: #666;
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 15px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .cta-section {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e, #16213e);
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    color: #d4af37;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #d4af37;
    color: white;
    padding: 12px 30px;
    border-radius: 25px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: all 0.3s;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background: #b8962f;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
</style>
